#  How Many Basic Types of Functions Are Available in Python?

There are two types of Functions in Python :-
    1) Built-in Function
    2) User Defined Function

1) Built-in Functions are Function that are already available in Python
ready to use. Just call them and use them.
e.g. print(),type(),len(),max(),...etc

2) User Defined Functions: We can create a Function of our own requirement using def keyword.
e.g. def greet()
        print "Hello"